Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:14.67,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追いつきたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.78,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然　物語
