Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}姐姐~姐姐~姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}新銳糕點師大賽 金獎蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}你也會變得幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:22.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}是我骨折
